			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3797526">
									

<p>I don't really care for the characterization of the Hand in this, as it seems a tad too &quot;mundane violence&quot; for their usual tastes (hearing that it was originally written as the CI makes it make a little more sense, though). That said, the SH <em>is</em> a very loose collective, so there's no real reason why this particular sect <em>couldn't</em> be like that.</p>
<p>I still just really love this entire concept you've introduced, and it tickles me that you were brave enough to actually include Fusion as a thing. I look forward to more dance-based duels in the future.</p>
<p>+1</p>

							</div>

								
